for_window $WINDOW_portal2     floating     disable
for_window $WINDOW_portal2     fullscreen
for_window $WINDOW_steam       layout       tabbed
for_window $WINDOW_kodi        layout       tabbed
for_window $WINDOW_spotify     layout       tabbed
